# Thoth local data.
#
# The markdown source-of-truth (MEMORY.md, LESSONS.md, skills/) can be
# committed alongside the repo. Everything else in `.thoth/` — the
# `graph.redb`, `fts.tantivy/`, `episodes.db`, `vectors.db`,
# `chunks.lance/`, and any legacy `index/` directory — is derivable and
# should never be tracked.
